  "important_notes": [
    "PostgresConnector supports exactly-once semantics (ExactlyOnceSupport.SUPPORTED)",
    "PostgresConnector validates read-only mode requires PG version >= 13",
    "PostgresConnection uses retry logic: up to 900 attempts with 2s pause for replication slot acquisition",
    "PostgresConnectorConfig.LogicalDecoder is an abstract enum - PGOUTPUT (supports truncate/logical decoding messages) vs DECODERBUFS (neither)",
    "PostgresOffsetContext tracks three LSN positions: current lsn (in SourceInfo), lastCompletelyProcessedLsn, lastCommitLsn, and optional streamingStoppingLsn",
    "SlotState is the SPI-layer data object (public API); ServerInfo.ReplicationSlot is the internal model",
    "PostgresOffsetContext.Loader supports read-only connections via PostgresReadOnlyIncrementalSnapshotContext"
  ]
